snippet.textDisplay: Magnificent pop music! Massive production job but crystal clear natural vocal recording with just enough presence.The song sits well with Gary Go's "Wonderful", for example. I reckon there will be some cool dance mixes. "Hell hath no fury..." when did you last hear those words in a power-pop-rock song? In the chorus, the writer includes the listener with the words : "This is the sound that we make", rather than "i" or "you" . I love the opening line of each verse - "Dear God..." This is a musical letter or prayer to the man upstairs! "We can't unlearn what we've learned". Masterful lyrics! Like I said, as I reach the end of the 3,45 mins. Perfect pop music! Just love @Biffy Clyro!

Congratulations for being my favourite band for almost 7 years now, all that time. ♥
